messages.messageBody:
Dear Friends,
I have just read and signed the petition:
For the Immediate Release of Andrei Love Spindell from Foster Care
and Return to His Natural Biologi
http://www.thePetitionSite.com/takeaction/818892804
Please help by signing this petition. It takes 30 seconds and will
really help. Please follow this link:
The system centralizes signature collection to provide consolidated,
useful reports for petition authors and targets. Please forward this
email to others you believe share your concern. To view additional
petitions, please click here:
http://www.thePetitionSite.com
Thank you
